column5: This is a preview of ari vinebergs new fishing show called The Fishin Life. The concept of the show is not about promoting new tackle and gear, but based around why people fish and why anglers become such "diehards". I thought many on the board would be interested. Im not exaclty sure if a network has picked the show up yet but I am pretty sure OLN is interested......     TDunn
Just remember that the action sequences happened 9-12 months ago eh!
